sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant T as Taker (XNO funder, OBX claimer)
    participant M as Maker (OBX funder, XNO sweeper)
    participant OBX as OBX chain
    participant XNO as XNO ledger

    Note over T,M: shares minted independently<br/>K=A+B, T=sA.G==Sa, account=(sA+sB).G
    T->>M: 1. Init (SwapID, A, Sa, PoP_A, Ra, T=sA.G, OBXamt, raw XNOamt, fee)
    Note over M: HandleInit: verify amounts+fee+PoP, derive K,R,account
    M->>T: 2. MakerCommit (B, Sb, PoP_B, Rb)
    Note over T: HandleMakerCommit: verify PoP_B, derive K, R=Ra+Rb, account

    M->>OBX: Fund SwapOut -> K (refund=B, bind ClaimR=R ClaimT=T, unlock h)
    OBX-->>M: SwapOut mined/confirmed
    M->>T: 3. Funded (SwapKey, UnlockHeight)
    T->>OBX: FindSwapOut + checkSwapOut (K, on-chain amount, window, R, T, refund=B)
    OBX-->>T: matches

    T->>XNO: Lock real XNO -> joint (sA+sB).G account
    XNO-->>T: lock id (cemented)
    T->>M: 4. XNOLocked (lock id)
    M->>XNO: Confirmed + LockInfo (dest account, amount)
    XNO-->>M: pays joint key, exact agreed amount

    T->>OBX: BuildClaim (unsigned claim tx -> core hash)
    T->>M: 5. ClaimRequest (core hash, s_a = ra + e.a)
    Note over M: verify s_a.G = Ra + e.A, one-coreHash nonce guard, store s_a
    M->>T: 6. ClaimPreSig (s_b = rb + e.b)

    Note over T: aggregate s_a+s_b, adapt with sA, verify full under K
    T->>OBX: MineClaim -> takes OBX, publishes S_full (reveals sA)
    T-->>M: (optional) ClaimDone hint - drained and ignored
    M->>OBX: FindSwapSpend (scrape published S_full)
    OBX-->>M: S_full
    Note over M: extract sA = S_full - s_a - s_b, recover sA+sB
    M->>XNO: Sweep joint -> maker sweep address
    XNO-->>M: swept , swap settled
